{
 "name": "RPlog_Into_the_Underworld",
 "title": "Into the Underworld",
 "summary": "Aboard the Tibanna Blues, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios tends a wretched Basca Starker as he purges the Sith Spawn of Vadim from himself, confessing the war crimes he committed without free will and admitting he fell for her in the desert. Determined to help, Jessalyn follows him into Hutt Space, boarding the Force-invisible vessel Jaded in Sov'Stayn's domain that the Select Committee granted him. In the eerie Cathedral Ichor he reveals his secret projects -- including a colony pod and a young clone of Johanna named Hanna who calls him 'uncle' -- and the two grow closer as they plan to scour the galaxy together for knowledge to fight Vadim and Malign. Their tense, intimate exchange ends almost domestically, Basca scooping a stunned, half-smiling Jessalyn into his arms as they consider the dangerous future ahead and the child she carries.",
